                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h4 class="accordion-toggle">What is your Refund and Cancellation Policy? </h4>
                                        <section class="accordion-inner panel-body">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Full payment must be made within 7 days of registration to hold a seat in the program</li>
                                                <li>Full refund, less $30 (administrative fee) if cancelled 15 days prior to start of class</li>
                                                <li>50% refund if cancelled 5 days prior to start of the class.</li>
                                                <li>No refund after that unless there is a wait list and the spot is filled.</li>
                                                <li>If the program is cancelled due to low enrollment, full refund will be made </li>
                                                <li>Students who are dismissed because of a rule violation, disciplinary reason or non-payment of late fee will not receive a refund. </li>
                                                <li>A fee of $30 will be assesses for any returned/declined payment transactions</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </section>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h4 class="accordion-toggle">What is the experience of your teachers?</h4>
                                        <section class="accordion-inner panel-body">
                                            <p>
                                              Our lead teachers are computer professionals with strong knowledge on the subject and has teaching experience. Some of out TA’s are high school of college students on CS path 

                                            </p>
                                        </section>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h4 class="accordion-toggle">Are the programs repeated in the same year?</h4>
                                        <section class="accordion-inner panel-body">
                                            <p>
                                                No. Each session new program is offered in the order of learning and skill building.  e.g. if Scratch level 1 is offered in session 1, Session 2 will be on Scratch level 2. So, the child can build on their skills learned in previous session and get a comprehensive knowledge of the tool/ language they are learning. 

                                            </p>
                                        </section>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h4 class="accordion-toggle">Are there any prerequisites for these programs?</h4>
                                        <section class="accordion-inner panel-body">
                                            <p>
                                               Yes, some of our programs have pre-requisites. Please check the Program Description page for more on pre-requisite. You can always contact us to discuss which program will best suit your child. 

                                            </p>
                                        </section>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h4 class="accordion-toggle">My child is highly capable. Can he join programs for grades higher than his/her? </h4>
