                                            <p>
                                                This can be done on approval from the teacher. At times some testing may be required depending the program. Please contact us to discuss.

                                            </p>
                                        </section>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h4 class="accordion-toggle">How can my child catch up on missed class?</h4>
