                                            <p>
                                                Thought we highly recommend not to miss any class as we cover a lot in each class. But circumstance do come, and we understand. Teacher will send link or email of what’s covered in the class with files for assignment and direction to complete at home. If needed and time permits will help the child complete the assignment later in the session
                                            </p>
                                        </section>
                                    </div>
